SIMPLE: main_street
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: main street
<hw>main street</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A main thoroughfare,
usually one in a small town having the largest concentration of retail
businesses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <specif>Hence:</specif> <mark>(Fig.)</mark> <def>The
attitudes, environment, or life style of a small town; -- usually
capitalized, and often used attributively; <as>as, <ex>Main Street</ex>
attitudes toward Washington</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mainswear</ent>⟦br⟧
